==ପ୍ରାକ୍ ଜୀବନ==
ଈଶା ଦେଓଲ ୨ ନଭେମ୍ବର ୧୯୮୧ ଦିନ ମୁମ୍ବାଇରେ (ପୂର୍ବତନ ବମ୍ବେ) ଜନ୍ମ ଗ୍ରହଣ କରିଥିଲେ ।<ref>{{Cite web| title = Esha Deol celebrates birthday with hubby and close friends| work = [[Mid Day]]| date = 4 November 2015| accessdate = 30 March 2016| url   = http://www.mid-day.com/articles/esha-deol-celebrates-birthday-with-hubby-and-close-friends/16653189}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web| title = I want Esha to have a baby soon: Hema Malini| work = [[The Indian Express]]| date = 2 November 2015| accessdate = 30 March 2016| url = http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/i-want-esha-to-have-a-baby-soon-hema-malini/}}</ref><ref name=Relations/> ବଲିଉଡ ଅଭିନେତା ଧର୍ମନ୍ଦ୍ର ଓ ହେମାମାଳିନୀଙ୍କର ସେ ବଡ଼ ଝିଅ । ତାଙ୍କର ସାନ ଭଉଣୀଙ୍କର ନାମ ଆହାନା । <ref name=Relations/><ref>{{cite news |last1=Shiksha |first1=Shruti |title=Esha Deol Reveals How Parents Hema Malini And Dharmendra Reacted To Her Second Pregnancy |url=https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/esha-deol-reveals-how-parents-hema-malini-and-dharmendra-reacted-to-her-second-pregnancy-1981429 |accessdate=16 January 2020 |work=NDTV.com |date=22 January 2019}}</ref> ସେ ବବି ଦେଓଲ ଓ ସନି ଦେଓଲଙ୍କର ସାବତ ଭଉଣୀ ଓ ଅଭୟ ଦେଓଲଙ୍କର ପ୍ରଥମ କଜିନ । <ref name=Relations>{{cite news |title=Esha Deol: Know about the actor's family members on her birthday |url=https://www.republicworld.com/entertainment-news/bollywood-news/esha-deols-family-members.html |accessdate=16 January 2020 |work=Republic World |date=2 November 2019}}</ref> ସେ ପିତାଙ୍କ ତରଫରୁ ପଞ୍ଜାବୀ ଓ ମାତାଙ୍କ ତରଫରୁ ତାମିଲ । <ref>{{cite news |title=My father is a die-hard Punjabi: Esha Deol |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/tv/my-father-is-a-die-hard-punjabi-esha-deol/story-Cc5brgoFKvXC52DxrR7MfP.html |accessdate=16 January 2020 |work=Hindustan Times |date=7 March 2015 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Happy Birthday Hema Malini: As original dream girl turns 71, see her family pics with Dharmendra, Esha Deol |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/bollywood/happy-birthday-hema-malini-as-original-dream-girl-turns-71-see-her-family-pics-with-dharmendra-esha-deol/story-zLAwJpHkknX7QJWOcUR7xL.html |accessdate=16 January 2020 |work=Hindustan Times |date=16 October 2019 |language=en}}</ref> ସେ ତାଙ୍କର ମାଆ ଓ ଭଉଣୀଙ୍କ ସ‌ହିତ ତାମିଲ ଭାଷାରେ କଥାବାର୍ତ୍ତା କରନ୍ତି । <ref>{{cite news |last1=Pradhan |first1=Bharathi S. |title=Esha Deol’s big fat wedding |url=https://www.telegraphindia.com/7-days/esha-deols-big-fat-wedding/cid/407170 |accessdate=16 January 2020 |work=www.telegraphindia.com |date=24 June 212 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Syed Firdaus Ashraf |title=I am today's woman: Esha Deol |url=https://www.rediff.com/movies/2004/may/19esha.htm |accessdate=16 January 2020 |work=www.rediff.com |date=19 May 2004}}</ref>

